#: ../../source/api/party_quotas_correction.rst:2
msgid "Party Quotas Correction"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction:1 of
msgid "Party quotas correction module."
msgstr "Modul zur Korrektur von Parteiquoten."

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction:3 of
msgid "This module handles the correction of party quotas to ensure that:"
msgstr "Dieses Modul behandelt die Korrektur von Parteiquoten, um sicherzustellen, dass:"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction:4 of
msgid "sum(quotas) == number_of_constituencies"
msgstr ""

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction:6 of
msgid ""
"The problem arises from integer division: sum(a_i // 2) <= sum(a_i) // 2 "
"When each party's seats are divided by 2 individually, we lose one quota "
"for each party with an odd seat count."
msgstr ""
"Das Problem entsteht durch ganzzahlige Division: sum(a_i // 2) <= "
"sum(a_i) // 2. Wenn die Sitze jeder Partei einzeln durch 2 geteilt werden, "
"geht für jede Partei mit ungerader Sitzanzahl eine Quote verloren."

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.correct_party_quotas:1 of
msgid ""
"Correct party quotas to ensure sum(quotas) == sum(seats) // 2. :param "
"quotas: Dictionary of base quotas (seats // 2 per party) :param seats: "
"Dictionary of seat counts per party :param strategy: "
"QuotaCorrectionStrategy enum value :param callback: Optional callback for"
" NEGOTIATED strategy :param rng: Optional random number generator for "
"probabilistic strategies :param seed: Optional seed for creating RNG if "
"rng is None"
msgstr ""
"Korrigiert Parteiquoten, damit sum(quotas) == sum(seats) // 2. :param "
"quotas: Wörterbuch der Basisquoten (seats // 2 pro Partei) :param seats: "
"Wörterbuch der Sitzanzahlen pro Partei :param strategy: "
"QuotaCorrectionStrategy-Enum-Wert :param callback: Optionaler Callback für "
"die NEGOTIATED-Strategie :param rng: Optionaler Zufallszahlengenerator für "
"probabilistische Strategien :param seed: Optionaler Seed zur Erstellung des "
"RNG, wenn rng None ist"

#: ../../source/api/party_quotas_correction.rst
msgid "Returns"
msgstr "Rückgabewert"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.correct_party_quotas:9 of
msgid "Corrected quotas dictionary"
msgstr "Wörterbuch der korrigierten Quoten"

#: ../../source/api/party_quotas_correction.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "Parameter"

#: ../../source/api/party_quotas_correction.rst
msgid "Return type"
msgstr "Rückgabetyp"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.select_parties_for_correction:1 of
msgid "Select which parties with odd seats should receive +1 to their quota."
msgstr "Wählt aus, welche Parteien mit ungerader Sitzanzahl +1 zu ihrer Quote erhalten sollen."

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.select_parties_for_correction:3 of
msgid "Dictionary of parties with odd seat counts"
msgstr "Wörterbuch der Parteien mit ungerader Sitzanzahl"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.select_parties_for_correction:4 of
msgid "Number of +1 corrections needed"
msgstr "Anzahl der benötigten +1-Korrekturen"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.select_parties_for_correction:5 of
msgid "QuotaCorrectionStrategy enum value"
msgstr "QuotaCorrectionStrategy-Enum-Wert"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.select_parties_for_correction:6 of
msgid "Optional callback for NEGOTIATED strategy"
msgstr "Optionaler Callback für die NEGOTIATED-Strategie"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.select_parties_for_correction:7 of
msgid "Optional random number generator for probabilistic strategies"
msgstr "Optionaler Zufallszahlengenerator für probabilistische Strategien"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.select_parties_for_correction:8 of
msgid "Optional seed for creating RNG if rng is None"
msgstr "Optionaler Seed zur Erstellung des RNG, wenn rng None ist"

#: ipres.party_quotas_correction.select_parties_for_correction:10 of
msgid "List of party names to receive +1"
msgstr "Liste der Parteinamen, die +1 erhalten"
